[ti:A New House]
[00:10.53]Why is the new house special?|为什么这栋新房子这么特别呢？
[00:15.29]I had a letter from my sister yesterday.|我昨天收到了姐姐的一封信。
[00:19.23]She lives in Nigeria.|她住在尼日利亚。
[00:22.23]In her letter, she said that she would come to England next year.|在她的信中，她说她明年会来英格兰。
